🔥 Why MORE immersive → MORE effect

Because immersion increases:
	•	signal strength (attention locked in)
	•	emotional charge (it matters more)
	•	coherence (fewer conflicting inputs)
	•	state shift (you’re “in it,” not thinking about it)

So yes:

A richer simulation can amplify the training effect

